{
  "stem": "10.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even the resistance I mentioned to you-- the people who were designated to go to the selections, to the gas chambers-- they had the strength yet to take off their clothes and leave it for other ones, just to help other ones, you see?",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is all resistance, because physically we couldn't resist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no arms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't fight in our camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Naturally, you know about Sobibor, the resistance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on in Auschwitz too, in Birkenau, where people who were serving in the gas chambers revolted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or the mines.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Mentioning about the mining.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My sister was working in the factory, in the ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from there they smuggled out in their handkerchiefs powder and gave it to the people working in the crematoriums and the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They made the bombs out of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Four girls were caught and were immediately hung.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were already on the transport going out of Auschwitz when they caught the four girls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They killed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My sister, they didn't catch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And other ones, not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My sister went on the transport like we, and was put in a car, in a train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And while the train was still standing, she noticed the other train on the other [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] railroad track, there were friends.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they waved her over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she jumped over to the other train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the Germans were looking all over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Already by fleeing, by going, by retreating, finding the other girls, they couldn't find her, because my sister was jumping from one train to another.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And fine, this I see, maybe Auschwitz, there are many things more.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what else can I tell you about Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
